        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Ezra 1:3",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ") by the edict, and the Jewish neighbours, not contemplated in the edict, who preferred to remain in the land of the Captivity.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
