      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] i.e. these gifts were over and above the free-will offerings. The clause in the original is peculiar, ‘beside over and above all ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "one",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
