        "text": " willingly offered’. The relative is omitted as in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Ezra 1:4",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", but is implied in ‘all’. The verb is active in meaning (cf. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Ezra 2:68",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
